title: Kanaa Kanden
subTitle: A young man comes up with a dream plan to help society, but he lacks the funds to complete the project. However, things take a turn when he meets a man who promises to finance his project.

title: Karuthamma
subTitle: A woman, who lives in a village where female infanticide is a common practice, goes to great lengths to get justice when her sister and her newborn child are murdered in cold blood.

title: Vallinam
subTitle: Due to a fatal accident, Krishna, a basketball player moves to a new college. There he locks horns with a Vamsi, a cricket maniac, who does not let other sports gain importance.

title: Jaisurya
subTitle: Surya, a fraudster, comes across an honest district collector, Jai, who is his lookalike. Things change when circumstances make him step into Jai's shoes.

title: Sengathu Boomiyile
subTitle: Vallarasu and Chinnasamy are two friends who come from closely related families. However, a fateful incident drives a wedge between them, culminating in a violent fight.

title: Thotti Jaya
subTitle: An orphan named Thotti Jaya is hired by a mobster after he is spotted thrashing a dishonest man. However, his troubles begin when he falls in love with his boss' daughter.

title: Yeidhavan
subTitle: When Krishna's sister is killed during a college protest, he vows to avenge her. However, he ends up helping the medical students to gain their rights.

title: Sachin
subTitle: A boy is named after Sachin Tendulkar, as his birth coincides with a celebratory day. As he grows older and falls for a woman named Anjali, he finds that they have a lot more in common than usual.
